  "design_notes": "A high-energy Hard (ITG-style 9) chart. S0/S1 introduces the rhythm with simple steps, ramping up as the tempo builds. S3 features a dense 8th-note stream and jumpstream on accents with layered vocal-hold freezes. S4 provides a breather with sparse taps. S5 drops into the second climax, utilizing drill textures and jumpstream with heavy hold integration in S9 and S11. S13 eases out with static steps to conclude the chart.",
